name: NewYorkCrew Association
goal: New York Crew association is composed of mixed members bringing together individuals who are interested in promoting public education through sports activities, the integration of large masses of youths in practicing and promoting these types of activities, creating a favorable current based on the development of sports consciousness and the development of events that facilitate practicing these activities.
euInitiatives: New York Crew follows the EU initiatives, policies and legislative files currently imposed by the Romanian legislation.
